    "Name": "Legionnaire",
    "Details": "The LGN-2K-RISC is a relatively barebones refit that simply swaps the standard 2K's primary weapon and MASC suite for a Hyper laser and additional heat sinks. This gives the Hyper laser an accurate and mobile delivery platform, without altering the visual profile of the more mundane LGN-2Kâ€”a field refit. Specially trained teams of RISC technicians and pilots were formed that traveled only with the refit kit, then met with existing line units utilizing stock LGN-2Ks to execute special missions. This ability to play shell games with hyper lasers served the Republic relatively well, with verified or suspected instances of LGN-2K-RISC deployments being more widespread than the limited production of the hyper laser would otherwise allow.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
